</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,458,151,210]" box="[151,359,186,210]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">
(Plate II, 
<figureCitation box="[256,350,186,210]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[151,249,1368,1391]" captionTargetBox="[199,1390,182,1345]" captionTargetId="figure-240@6.[188,1398,169,1371]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Gurawa truncata sp. nov. A: male pygofer side, lateral view; B: valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D: connective, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view, respectively." pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Figure 3</figureCitation>
